Description:
malloc() function that is glibc compatible.

Files:
lib/malloc.c

Depends-on:
malloc-posix
xalloc-oversized     [test $REPLACE_MALLOC_FOR_MALLOC_GNU = 1]

configure.ac:
gl_FUNC_MALLOC_GNU
if test $REPLACE_MALLOC_FOR_MALLOC_GNU = 1; then
  AC_LIBOBJ([malloc])
fi
gl_STDLIB_MODULE_INDICATOR([malloc-gnu])

Makefile.am:

Include:
<stdlib.h>

